                  <handDesc>
                     <p>Ýmsar hendur.</p>
                     <p>14r-15r: Jón Ólafsson (sbr. 15r).</p>
                  </handDesc>
                  <musicNotation>
                     <p>Nótur við sálm á bl. 14r-15r.</p>
                  </musicNotation>
